7d80733b-c7dc-4d9f-9397-e49f2ec665e1	SENI BUDAYA WAYANG GOLEK	salah hiji kasenénbudaya sunda anu populer dimasyarakat urangkiwari nyeta wayang golek. komo, ggeus bisa disérkeu dinaradio televisi, wayang golek tepi dipikaresep be ku balarea, bohdikota, boh dilemburan. lamun kali aya nu hajat tanggap wayng golek, nu lalajo tehilahatna sok tumplek dimana mendi. atuh tokoh tokoh dinapawayangan apan geus dipikawanoh ku masyarakat urang, upamanabe gatotgaca, arjuna bima, dotna, semar,  cepot, jeug sajabana. wayang golek teh hiji pagelaran anu mangrupa gabungansababaraha unsur kasenén, nyeta seni sastra(lalakon),senikarawitan(gamelan), seni sora(sinden), jeung seni gerak atawatari(gerak-gerik wayang) anu jadi lulugu dina pagelaran.wayang goleknyeta dalang anu pancen ngalakonkeun carita. kamanerandalang, ngigulkeun parasipah atwa bodor. kulantaran kitu dalang tehdiperdih pisan kamaheranana dina rupa-rupa widang. salé ti nyegelkeun wayang-wayang, dlang oge ngagunakeun parabotsejen nyeta campala, jeung kecrek. camapala teh bangsa palu anosok ditakolkeun, nepikeun nantebkeun hiji omong atawa hijiperistiwa anu keur dilalakonkeun. disagedekeun lang, nayaga ogenyekel kalunggunan anu penting. apan nayaga pisan nabeuhgamelan teh.	https://www.scribd.com/document/385246934/Artikel-Bahasa-Sunda	146	[-0.48567182,-0.21772936,-0.07630621,0.22237356,0.19029638,-0.059006028,-0.091704294,0.06697389,0.15570702,0.26585522,-0.2570805,0.603196,0.014730881,-0.4767454,0.38259733,-0.28349352,0.079697125,-0.18777126,0.61613876,-0.24255824,-0.14136231,0.009710282,-0.079930514,0.39499027,0.08102143,-0.055552006,-0.23539832,0.71289116,0.36091343,-0.18833807,0.39957207,-0.19019774,0.16747542,-0.24889632,-0.11811807,-0.031664204,0.032493394,-0.071394995,-0.1443548,-0.036785796,0.16967347,0.12569655,-0.24079394,0.5355758,0.24382204,-0.034061395,0.16777287,-0.27680126,-0.099733725,-0.3092234,0.023476547,-0.17847823,-0.34205356,-0.4261415,0.46549198,-0.48037973,0.6716725,0.22702834,-0.28514415,-0.18041982,