, tah nu sok makanan lér oge moal aya. 3. ngagunakeun barang nu ramah lingkung tah urang salarea lamun nyah kana lingkung hirup urang kudu bisa ngagunakeun barang nu ramah lingkung nu bisa sababaraha kali pake kawas lamun balanjateh pake kantong bésa we ulah pake kantong plastik anu tambah nambahan sampah nu lila koraina. tah sok geura malamalalikir ngagunakeun bahan nu ramah lingkung meh tetep jaga lingkung hirup urang. 4. tek kendaran umum euleuh naha jol kana kendaran umum? sok gera tebak naha bet jadi kana kendaran umum sagala? tah ku loba kendaran pribadi loba oge polusi nu dikalorkeun kudunamah urangteh pake kendaran umum, naha bet kitu? ari pake kendaran mah urangteh la hemat béya ditambahkan ramah keur lingkung anda, tah polusiteh bisa ngurangan sahenteuna teu kawan mawa kendaran sorangan. kasimpulana mule lingkung hirupteh kewajiban nu hirup genah hnteuna diri urang jeung lingkung urang kumaha urangna, jadi lamun hayang sam kop geura mumule lingkung hirupna.	http://tipscaras.blogspot.com/2017/01/contoh-artikel-bahasa-sunda-tentang-lingkungan-hidup.html	464	[-0.4374811,-0.28631294,0.109774075,0.31926775,-0.039938524,-0.26866186,-0.23048526,-0.122344196,0.19598427,0.2704751,-0.48421955,0.50618815,0.15786538,-0.57648194,0.33216125,-0.17780448,0.22210993,-0.19308186,0.6421619,-0.038893253,-0.016405923,0.05985102,-0.054745845,0.28749615,-0.21318257,-0.20769134,-0.07629272,0.58433735,0.24080463,-0.17206647,0.37216425,-0.1537492,0.2218839,-0.43211043,-0.037485708,-0.032363232,-0.034822572,0.028912589,-0.33845338,0.04973908,-0.08447403,-0.05919115,-0.31916848,0.39560947,0.2863463,0.1895932,0.16370165,-0.15712735,0.1686178,-0.31532532,-0.047955234,-0.12846114,-0.37335956,-0.35952973,0.24053445,-0.45519453,0.5631677,-0.021042753,-0.16979083,-0.18985824,0.10799827,0.030291544,0.21117198,0.07245425,-0.25442225,-0.055178896,0.26405352,-0.0043366235,-0.59905493,-0.00884751,-0.22176293,0.08837509,-0.4118407,-0.3067968,-0.0064941724,-0.042309113,0.03890195,0.61069614,0.226