 bener, nyeta jalan nu lempeng. hirup urang atur pipiti gugah bobo nempika bade bobo oge, non buktosna? tah coba gugah bobo pasti urang do heula kitu oge sateocan bobo pasti doa heula, bat asup kana wc oge pan urangteh doa heula, yen etateh salah hiji bentuk kepercayan urang ka maha pencipta. kasimpulanana agamateh aya aneh katur hirup urang meh hirup urangteh henteu joh tina jalan nu bener, pan hirup urang aneh aya pamuntanganana nyeta ka alloh. inget oge a gama katur meh hirup jalma dinya teu co balo, meh pada pada ngarti, pada pada apal kumaha kuduna, kumaha nyatana.	http://tipscaras.blogspot.com/2017/02/contoh-artikel-bahasa-sunda-tentang-agama.html	430	[-0.3712238,-0.25709242,-0.035954833,0.39917728,0.053173788,-0.26128983,-0.17450279,0.017672129,0.0739806,0.07943614,-0.41362542,0.32372946,0.054479316,-0.4135062,0.27446976,-0.21263015,0.14320329,-0.033684924,0.5987768,-0.14676763,-0.019058958,0.13631302,-0.051054806,0.19996792,-0.08467059,-0.16102353,-0.13246067,0.67717755,0.36461413,-0.100257255,0.32423872,-0.17074785,0.09945765,-0.3595296,-0.044649888,-0.10091987,0.10734273,-0.051910408,-0.3436187,0.033817764,0.1299422,-0.041169316,-0.41558713,0.3913616,0.17270818,-0.049884014,0.22090125,-0.30035725,0.20454836,-0.3773681,-0.008017346,-0.22825262,-0.31026262,-0.2633983,0.3040095,-0.4744168,0.56931686,0.18069091,-0.32718083,-0.13175479,0.14206825,-0.07154817,0.12304416,0.075779825,-0.04378499,-0.00058583263,0.3665945,0.14327666,-0.41497108,-0.05512183,-0.09028175,-0.01752672,-0.21201228,-0.060801208,-0.06970218,-0.023560137,0.12407916,0.6931577,0.28770667,0.3797248,-0.26629984,-0.26380682,0.00021060882,0.12563208,-0.20070915,0.34490043,0.1316438,0.42936262,0.071977064,-0.04623002,0.32076523,-0.22049265,0.24331656,0.0621682,-0.33127576,0.43034708,-0.19295943,-0.00870106,0.01274345,0.5931567,0.7919744,0.20561184,0.23520163,-0.08752945,-0.07024493,-0.15860769,-0.4284,0.7058803,-0.15102738,-0.060434297,0.2612056,-0.56758934,-0.06704238,-0.040946,0.46713513,0.142608