b164f2b2-32a8-412e-94f0-1fbfedbb8f1d	Seureuh Ubar Kampung Urang Sunda	urang sunda geus ti baheula wawuh jeung serureh (piper betle). seureuh teh aya rupa rupa, nya tea seureuh jawa, rupa hideung sarta leuwih lada; seureuh nu rada beureum uratna, ngan tikuhur; jeung seureuh nu hejo uratna. seureuh mangrupa tutuwuhan nu ngarambat, don sari lada, sok pake nyeupah jeung pake ubar. sanajan kiwari wanoja nu ngora langka nyeupah, tapi seureuh masih aya keneh dijarolan di tukang rampe. seureuh bisa mangpat atahna, oge bisa olah heula jadi minyak. lamun aya nu raheut, bisa dibalurak ku minyak seureuh atawa bisa oge don seureuh dirieus, campur apu tik, tuluy ditaplokkeun ka nu raheutna. pikeun ubar nyeri panon, ruhna sabada kumbah beresih, tuluy gelang tinyuh ku cétah. eta cai seureuh teh pake meresihan panon nu nyeri tea. pikeun ubar batuk, don seureuh rieus campur apu, tuluy balur aka beuheung. anu nyeri dada oge bisa ubar ku seureuh nu meunang ngarieus kira kira lima lambar, campur ku minyak hades, apu, cai jeruk nipis, kina tipung, jeung bawang beureum sapotong. seureuh matak kot kana huntu. ku kituna, nu sok rajin nyeupah mah langka anu nyeri huntu. jadi, pangaruh gede pisan. dina iklan odol (pasta gigi) aya anu pake don seureuh minangka salahiji bahanna. kitu deuhi seureuh sok pake paranti kekemu (obat kumur). lén ti eta, nu bo baham oge bisa kurang ku reuh, ku cara beuweung lambar atawa do lambar reuh. mun bisa mah seureuh nu beuweung tadi teh terus diteureuy. mangpat don seureuh bisa oge keur ngubaran saréwan. panyakit saréwan dina istilah urang sunda, bésa sok tanda ku lor getih tina léng pangambung. dina basa indonesé mah sebut mimisan. cara ngubarana, don seureuh pintel pintel, jiga aki urang nu sok leukeun keneh ngaroko pake don kawung. don seureuh ge pintel pintel jiga kitu. tuluy don seureuh nu meunang pintel pintel tea teh cocok kana pangambung. insya allow, moal lami deui oge getih bakal sat. kiwari geus langka wanoja sunda nu nyeupah. kitu ge geus karolot pisan. ku kituna, seureuh geus teu pati dipikawanoh mangpat ku nu ngarora. padahal dina seureuh teh loba zat nu aya mangpat pikeun awak urang.	https://www.burung-net.com/2015/06/contoh-artikel-bahasa-sunda-tentang-kesehatan-sirih.html	343	[-0.53549606,-0.32570106,0.0058969352,0.26812983,0.07076091,-0.27490097,-0.1477283,-0.02221305,0.038784675,0.31650534,-0.49315813,0.5722579,0.093400076,-0.59886086,0.3016768,-0.25998512,0.38272947,-0.12609252,0.7215596,0.028734872,-0.0884324,0.12494466,-0.008851028,0.4173382,-0.045081373,-0.15834482,-0.10869397,0.705181,0.31540602,-0.25135976,0.3170249,-0.25189087,0.13911851,-0.35936528,-0.0982603,0.10279447,0.15804586,-0.08180961,-0.12206773,-0.073316164,-0.054906994,-0.0004966501,-0.19326165,0.49273515,0.20392081,0.24858813,0.18077579,-0.25126737,0.118051544,-0.5200807,0.13339886,-0.17094755,-0.44002205,-0.3879174,0.3333594,-0.53769433,0.59177494,0.010797412,-0.19134276,-0.12982836,0.09697883,0.016857006,0.18581039,0.089329004,-0.16022477,0.054476425,0.33475423,0.16814497,-0.53312147,-0.08775707,-0.24593443,0.12363162,-0.1864636,-0.08137087,-0.17552122,0.033246465,-0.0023631775,0.740687,0.16207421,0.3447646,-0.13249741,-0.26209715,0.09336533,0.2581995,-0.3397562,0.54429674,-0.03824661,0.49225074,0.14189869,0.15820876,0.14862402,-0.38513517,-0.029859511,-0.10477044,-0.34929988,0.27920458,-0.34780604,-0.25853252,0.13264869,0.60879433,0.5256238,0.21613324,0.18327005,-0.070692085,-0.011464294,-0.23606527,-0.39480016,0.34478933,0.020282328,-0.052152157,0.41874093,-0.4189366,-0.09396971,-0.14797343,0.6511074,0.20631161,-0.02791574,0.24196053,0.0513191,-0.23492545,-0.45604277,0.17959103,-0.10885472,-0.0368768,-0.18122378,0.16697127,0.05034758,-0.09497379,0.6392281,-0.09806199,0.19294986,0.2773612,0.12978327,-0.014763661,0.07248271,-0.45039237,0.47069705,0.29793215,-0.3724612,0.28642237,-0.27369207,-0.6624764,-0.07671297,-0.3065366,-0.119921006,0.2347739,0.4892584,-0.42059356,-0.15526672,0.5031937,-0.3047601,0.0075432574,0.15312976,-0.03063