 kampung naga urang moal manggihan jamban atawa pacilingan di jero atawa di gigir imah. mandi jeung pacilingan teh jieun di walungan, lantaran cenah imah kudu jon tina tempat kokotor. pikeun jaga alam sabudeureun, di kampung naga oge aya nu isebut leuweung larangan. ieu leuweung perenah di tonggoh walungan ciwulan, lega welas hektar. ieu leuweung te riksa ku sarerea kah henteu ruksak, maksud minangka sumber cai. lamun leuweung tetep dipéra, sumber cai moal sat sarta dina usum hujan moal banjir.	https://www.galerisurat.com/2023/01/contoh-artikel-bahasa-sunda.html	397	[-0.5680071,-0.4190213,0.05243527,0.39291024,0.04825155,-0.12633732,-0.2158181,-0.045600258,0.16061169,0.2338347,-0.4923498,0.5745415,0.12503073,-0.6800277,0.30280715,-0.36027172,0.13155454,-0.18597598,0.5934346,-0.061746176,-0.13413835,0.093663394,0.050146807,0.3186725,0.061920784,-0.20910096,-0.22958821,0.6314194,0.24212685,-0.24668127,0.44105572,-0.2328659,0.11077412,-0.27836496,0.015353765,-0.10947707,0.08265056,-0.06156741,-0.33900347,0.003841091,0.1153347,-0.019510306,-0.26571813,0.5727805,0.10544309,-0.006096699,0.23687205,-0.17644426,0.12084359,-0.31219786,0.052857272,-0.22873192,-0.31406298,-0.2698465,0.27124804,-0.5370582,0.5302759,0.039097004,-0.34516877,-0.22575498,0.19454353,-0.026808811,0.14252403,0.13618474,-0.09799832,0.025658567,0.3302161,0.0547022,-0.34209645,-0.006833194,-0.16547388,0.057923093,-0.37991,-0.005882334,-0.16662078,0.015162166,0.08177852,0.5360948,0.09928987,0.41628107,-0.12071885,-0.06937876,0.23584269,0.25356042,-0.26599222,0.28156516,-0.10396405,0.5424973,0.18765056,0.16092384,0.24791992,-0.20635357,0.18264529,-0.044052448,-0.34360635,0.3196227,-0.23336594,-0.12585057,0.14956592,0.5750569,0.5562353,0.04353492,0.23449682,-0.10616988,-0.19360885,-0.24085522,-0.28008568,0.48638844,-0.02475492,-0.10232271,0.3145049,-0.27602446,0.022375703,-0.21783358,0.42235792,0.23252916,-0.018132735,0.20353504,-0.09986044,-0.08333339,-0.45177668,0.11518188,-0.19166705,-0.068868145,-0.3136