3cd3d9cc-fa9a-4694-aa80-5f145ca2d461	Sajarah Pamarentahan Kota Bogor	punjul kota bogor ti kota-kota sejen nu aya di jawa barat nyeta kasang tukang sajarahna. pangna kitu lan di bogor kungsi deg karajan pajajaran. di dieu pisan prabu liwangi, raja pajajaran anu mashur kungsi ngaheuyeuk dayeuh ngolah nagara. ku sabab raket kait jeung sajarah pajajaran, arti upama pamarentah kota bogor nangtukeun identitas derah teh tina istiwa sajarah pajajaran. upama be dina nangtukeun “hari jadi” kota bogor, pamarentah derah netepkeun dina tanggal 3 juni 1482. ieu teh dasar kana sajarah ngadegna puseur dayeuh karajan pajajaran. karajan pajajaran pingpin ku sri duga maharaja anu telah prabu liwangi. sri duga mimiti cangking kalungguhan raja pajajaran dina to 1482 sarta langsung lila 39 ton. anu jadi ibukota karajan nyeta pakon. tah, ti dinya pisan, tina istiwa paku jadi puseur pamarentahan anu jadi titik indit itung ton “hari jadi” teh. ditetepkeunana angka ton 1482 dasar kana ulikan sajarah yen sri duga maharaja mimiti deg jadi raja pajajaran teh dina ton 1482. ari nangtukeun tanggal jeung bulan dasar kana carita pantun bogor. dina pantun bogor aya bagi carita “ngahiyangna pajajaran” anu nyaritakeun yen baheula di ibukota pajajaran sok ayak upacara kuwerabakti. ieu upacara teh maksud ngareoh-reoh atawa sukur usum panen, lila 9 poe. rame pisan ieu pesta rahayat teh, luuhan ku para inohong karajan jeung kum rahayat pajajaran. dina ton 1482, upacara kuwerabakti teh ayak dina tanggal 3 juni. lén ti ngareoh-reoh usum panen, oge bari sakalén ngaresmikeun paku minangka puseur dayeuh (ibu kota) karajan pajajaran. eta sabab tanggal 13 juni 1482 tuluy tetep jadi “hari jadi” kota bogor. lén ti nangtukeun “hari jadi”, pamarentah kota bogor oge netepkeun lambang, minangka identitas anu mandiri. titen ieu lambang kota bogor wangun ‘perisai’ segi lima. dina eta perisai aya opat gambar nyeta: 1) manuk galudra anu nuduhkeun lambang nagara, 2) gunung salak puncak opat anu nuduhkeun yen kota bogor perenah aya di suku gunung salak, 3) istana bogor anu nuduhkeun yen kota bogor boga tempat (istana) anu kandung sajarah, jeung 4) kujang anu nuduhkeun yen kota bogor minangka ‘barang pusaka’ waris karajan pajajaran. kotamadya bogor oge boga motto, nyeta di nu kiwari ngancik nu bihari, seja ayeuna sampeur jaga, anu harti non-non anu karasa ku urang poe ieu teh hasil usaha poe kamari, jeung non anu dipigawe ku urang poe ieu mangrupa tarekah pikeun hontal poe isuk nu leuwih punjul. kota bogor sép tandang dina pangwangunan, pikeun ngawujudkeun program “kota jeroeun taman”.	https://basasunda.com/sajarah-pamarentahan-kota-bogor/	394	[-0.35716844,-0.31096786,0.14311576,0.17567486,0.028621875,-0.08965835,-0.29511565,0.10043972,0.21703982,0.24036217,-0.59375805,0.7016189,0.19289243,-0.75848746,0.088908,-0.26724178,0.25044942,-0.31671613,0.53690004,-0.12847933,-0.23576921,0.29317155,0.08199687,0.3406085,-0.20100175,-0.19962975,-0.16704121,0.5384688,0.27277315,-0.18348955,0.31273705,-0.17616314,0.09310375,-0.28456932,0.032340985,0.046052422,0.023273345,0.08481302,-0.25076127,-0.043521088,0.15534028,0.20232293,-0.28046545,0.5747926,0.27953315,-0.15877539,0.23118171,-0.2864879,-0.09371858,-0.22959217,0.10842813,-0.23823607,-0.39121318,-0.3959607,0.21960431,-0.5360259,0.6395198,0.22507018,-0.25476924,-0.029232766,0.113394,-0.055655323,0.17805015,0.07546965,0.011556009,-0.008473434,0.2145144,-0.0688199,-0.39562833,-0.14006603,-0.00015414692,0.32656008,-0.292809,0.0020649992,-0.2566836,-0.005296031,0.00035019405,0.46231776,0.21616244,0.3359224,-0.1505698,-0.17254537,0.38097304,0.3301854,-0.33640367,0.16092092,-0.10413326,0.4647538,0.2823674,0.17665774,0.23879802,-0.15551405,0.22737142,-0.082498685,-0.2698964,0.28596884,-0.09448908,-0.11382611,0.15006664,0.522238,0.594312,0.014252385,0.24888375,0.029334107,-0.29044288,-0.021263272,-0.25764734,0.3936531,-0.066126436,-0.1494013,0.29531968,-0.47223082,0.05021316,-0.1884602,0.3917563,0.22131139,0.130279,0.228667,-0.23721917,-0.088824764,-0