 menhir ukuranana 2,1 méter sarta 2,2 méter. dasar informasi anu katampa, rorongkong éta téh, manusa ti mangsa ahir prasejarah (kira-kira abad ka-2 atawa ka-3 masehi), saméméh mangsa candi di lokasi éta anu asup kana adab jaman karajan tarumanagara. hal éta sampak ti bekel kubur anu panggih dina layon, nyéta gabah sarta pakakas-pakakas tina logam atawa beusi anu mangrupa pakakas milik jelema anu dikubur.	http://majalah-balebat.blogspot.com/2010/05/ahli-carangka-itb-diturunkeun.html	344	[-0.5582597,-0.3325025,0.112369165,0.31964615,0.24570772,-0.058777772,-0.29120126,0.04165178,0.21261859,0.19936241,-0.6583921,0.58153856,0.021083776,-0.4640665,0.22785117,-0.16079119,0.26332283,-0.24601135,0.5939801,-0.11871343,-0.24343652,0.096363224,0.15238789,0.157623,0.0076214895,-0.1783322,-0.16142374,0.62315744,0.19729704,-0.20455515,0.5144778,-0.13510655,0.14166044,-0.35238463,0.12910779,-0.018386643,0.1321925,-0.00094670686,-0.20610666,0.1514962,0.19890636,0.26867285,-0.22196855,0.511247,0.22724913,-0.13306147,0.22789289,-0.28540197,0.06716544,-0.20675544,0.017097607,-0.13455862,-0.4175281,-0.26918977,0.47725892,-0.4584809,0.6723825,0.09839564,-0.17573652,-0.15598994,0.2220878,-0.022800732,0.3012989,0.15122184,-0.084240444,-0.14140432,0.36091024,-0.10192914,-0.41726148,-0.22231561,-0.22806865,0.053907536,-0.5382485,-0.083358504,-0.06761781,0.03113562,0.011282034,0.5016487,0.09487729,0.44273907,-0.16800195,-0.12846996,0.41685003,0.33319432,-0.3517236,0.14438784,-0.17906895,0.60224026,0.0058743227,0.17269391,0.15768044,-0.27970797,0.20472395,0.032242987,-0.23192522,0.357869,-0.32081434,-0.20792902,0.35894418,0.50155324,0.5561776,-0.011752985,0.13921614,-0.052564826,-0.14716956,-0.17208393,-0.25933677,0.4292069,-0.013348806,0.006824728,0.2873286,-0.37230635,-0.014549313,-0.27834672,0.3955477,0.28723258,0.058621183,0.063876,-0.14635336,-0.14156233,-0.45862442,0.07935588,-0.15423962,-0.07484199,-0.24784389,0.17147973,0.02514521,-0.1651848,0.32165527,-0.069303796,0.1132063,0.1439696