 ti tu karut anu boga gorowong (ceruk). ceuk katerangan penduduk, baheula di lebah gorowong ieu sok dipaké ku jalma keur tatapa. di handap gorowong ieu ogé tempo aya do tu anu rata anu diperkirakeun guna pikeun tempat diuk nu tatapa sarta keur teundeun sasaji. ékskavasi laku tepi 100 cm ka jero taneuh ca vértikal. tina léng nu kali ieu ngan panggih hiji duit récéh (koin) arab. koin arab ieu gambar téh samar pisan, teu jelas non rupana. hingga tepi ka poéan sosélisasi gé can nyaho ti jaman mana asalna koin arab ieu. nurul ogé ngajéntrékeun, panalungtikan di kawas ndangbarang ieu mangrupa panalungtikan awal, anu baris tuluy dina ton-ton anu bakal tang. "ku kitu teu anéh mun hasil panalungtikan ieu masih kénéh joh tina harepan, da kakara ngaléngkah pisan," pungkasna.	http://majalah-balebat.blogspot.com/2010/10/balar-bandung-ngagelar-sosialisasi.html	409	[-0.4848626,-0.27958947,0.09691305,0.32158655,0.21979974,-0.124178454,-0.32327074,-0.024850799,0.33147752,0.23260204,-0.55286366,0.5691837,0.09667617,-0.569,0.23358765,-0.32288608,0.13882203,-0.18926172,0.5542753,-0.1728698,-0.112864025,0.097641915,0.15472543,0.320008,-0.1664755,-0.22055402,-0.12818488,0.59595,0.17396899,-0.20351243,0.42215243,-0.23658271,0.22567905,-0.33500677,0.084490106,0.012441257,0.19775116,-0.06514956,-0.22088665,0.00034387782,0.289851,0.18451889,-0.21196312,0.48000038,0.07533697,-0.18371421,0.18338138,-0.19682646,-0.05526413,-0.23150459,0.13256577,-0.12945929,-0.37767816,-0.3170486,0.46837714,-0.45494562,0.50321925,0.09290968,-0.28951806,-0.25162435,0.17645162,-0.042109046,0.1495711,-0.009529427,-0.064690076,-0.030558567,0.37150583,0.02763897,-0.4112439,-0.27889666,-0.14106895,0.073390335,-0.414005,-0.05543826,-0.21469644,-0.049429394,0.007380034,0.5666518,0.18460849,0.31595188,-0.22390378,-0.27061495,0.47844183,0.2510444,-0.28487474,0.02170956,-0.0824199,0.60678387,0.13479052,0.28205013,0.21777241,-0.22534035,0.23189399,0.041953906,-0.26502734,0.30467096,-0.27813703,-0.12520641,0.2591396,0.51713