38fe7c40-ab82-4f6e-bfa9-2ddf013d4c7b	Babalayan di Gunung Batu	di wilayah bogor méh teu itung patilasan-patilasan karuhun urang nu maké kecap 'batu'. conto bé tu karaton di ciburél tugu utara, tu kembar di cikereteg caringin, tu layang jeung tu kasur di cisaro, tu karut jeung tu korsi di ndangbarang pasir eurih, jeung réa-réa deui. patilasan-patilasan tadi mangrupa hiji tu nu gedé (monolit). aya deui batu-batu nu susun mangrupa bénténg atawa kuta, saperti kuta gegelang di gunung bunder, jero kuta di tu tulis. ogé aya nu mangrupa bénténg-bénténg atawa téras tu pikeun tah galengan, saperti nu panggih di kota tu jeung ndangbarang. lén ti éta, aya wangunan-wangunan tu anu susun atawa balay undak-undakan tepi ka siga gugunungan, di tengah bésa aya tangga tepi ka undak pangluhurna, sarta bésa di dinya sok aya ménhir atawa tu tangtung. wangun tu modél kitu téh ilah sebut pundén, wangun tu berundak, atawa téras berundak. conto bé arca domas di pasir muncang (baheula mah cikopo selatan), léngkob di tapos, pasir karamat di calobak, pasir manggis (ténjolaya), jeung sababaraha deui nu aya di kompléks cibalay (tenjolaya). nurutkeun r.von heine-geldem (1926) tradisi sieun bénténg-bénténg batu, tu tangtung (ménhir), ogé pundén asup tradisi mégalitik to, nu mimiti gelar kira-kira 2500-1500 ton sm. tuluy mégalitik to téh ku manéhna asup kana masa atawa jaman néolitikum awal (jaman tu baru). urang bisa niténan patilasan-patilasan anu aya di wewengkon bogor dina buku r.d.m. verbeek (1891) nu judul lijst voor voornamste overblijfselen uit den hindoutijd op java. lén ti éta ogé dina lapor oudheidkundigen dienst (dinas kapurbakalan) nu diterbitkeun dina ton 1914 nu susun ku n.j. krom. patilasan di gunung tu gunung tu keur urang bogor mah ga moal bireuk nyéta mangrupa ngaran tempat nu ayeuna asup ka kecamatan kota bogor barat. ngan mun tilik ka béh tukang, baheula gunung tu téh hiji wilayah anu lumayan lega. beulah kulon wates jeung ndangbarang, beulah wétan wates téh jembatan cisadané, beulah kalér wates ku kampung tari kolot, sedeng di beulah kidul wates jeung pasir kuda ciomas. kusabab aya pamekaran, gunung tu kiwari bagi jadi sababaraha kelurahan, di anta kelurahan gunung tu (tetep maké ngaran heubeulna), kelurahan pasir mulya, jeung kelurahan loji. malah jalan gunung tu ogé ayeuna mah geus robah jadi jalan mayjén ishak djorsa. tug tepi ka kiwari rupa can aya nu ngajelaskeun naha tempat éta téh sebut gunung batu. kumaha jujutanana? naha aya gunung nu ji tina tu atawa tu nu badega siga gunung?	http://majalah-balebat.blogspot.com/2012/06/normal-0-false-false-false.html	392	[-0.6876098,-0.16998583,0.044181366,0.37888205,0.040836774,-0.0692198,-0.19597852,0.12188572,0.08564651,0.21879768,-0.358926,0.529704,0.24676022,-0.53983384,0.17861347,-0.32881373,0.26928693,-0.18685651,0.49223587,-0.24308974,-0.2422736,-0.0044599846,0.12976894,0.0598573,-0.124826774,-0.18145628,-0.15400289,0.48414436,0.30203652,-0.089530826,0.43061233,-0.16643067,0.28770614,-0.2596938,0.11656703,-0.07533876,0.30978185,-0.011520736,-0.38530692,0.008630118,0.17353761,0.18459189,-0.15709227,0.6609815,0.22239295,-0.0259636,0.17973459,-0.16088806,-0.026312899,-0.3460284,-0.0032044123,-0.05258286,-0.43735796,-0.3518047,0.30563757,-0.45622206,0.5641967,-0.029967455,-0.20465276,-0.18821205,0.15494432,0.07622701,0.29099584,-0.024290416,-0.13617271,-0.027648043,0.46811074,-0.072811306,-0.3230515,0.032253932,-0.2343036,0.04977999,-0.54040927,-0.07659805,-0.23019949,-0.016485702,0.08867156,0.44974262,0.16986986,0.41351354,-0.19293055,-0.058041632,0.36782628,0.04802537,-0.18265505,0.13741992,-0.29173484,0.42003506,0.069937855,0.2175235,0.19819254,-0.3302093,0.29179108,0.033135563,-0.19338256,0.21495122,-0.44336808,-0.05596438,0.23603877,0.5283064,0.5261326,-0.011718031,0.18483171,-0.04239315,-0.102646865,-0.16927221,-0.3696925,0.37041718,0.08477634,0.018382639,0.18779837,-0.452555,-0.07705398,-0.25572035,0.45671862,0.3472069,0.075451195,0.2652455,-0.17432654,-0.27031595,-0.4911459,0.01560778