020b5c78-a51c-4134-bd8e-40a5b9f9b3c0	Aya Taman Sri Bagénda di Pasir Eurih	mimiti poé jum’ah (5/4) tim arkéolog nu bentuk ku dines budaya jeung pariwisata kabupatén bogor bakal talungtik gunung sodong di désa karéhkél, kecamatan leuwiléng, kabupatén bogor. tim ieu baris digawé tepi ka poé ahad (14/4). tim arkéolog ieu mangrupa gabungan ti sawatara instansi di antarana: jurusan arkeologi fib universitas indonésé (8 urang) nu pingpin ku dr. cécép éka permana; dr. johan arif, géolog ti itb; anton ferdénto ti balai arkéologi bandung; héndra p asti ti riksa sunda institute bogor; indri, arkéolog disbudpar kabupatén bogor; sarta ti balai pelestarén peninggalan purbakala (bp3) sérang (2 urang). rencana tim panalungtik baris ngalakukeun ékskavasi di do atawa tilu lokasi di budeur gunung sodong. ogé ngalakukeun survey muka di sawatara tempat nu boga tuduh awal aya kagétan jalma mangsa baheula, asup bakal taliti kayan guha-guha nu aya di dinya. tim panalungtik digawé dasar lapor ti tim survéy lapang nu bentuk ku disbudpar kabupatén bogor bulan agustus ton 2012. harita, tim survéy eusi ku panalungtik ti balai arkéologi bandung, bp3 sérang, jeung téknik géologi itb.	http://majalah-balebat.blogspot.com/2012/07/aya-taman-sri-bagenda-di-pasir-eurih.html	169	[-0.56831306,-0.19269557,0.1492077,0.2562958,0.24551946,-0.09759539,-0.19334523,-0.112795494,0.20070636,0.07423178,-0.6459445,0.515846,-0.01819206,-0.5572478,0.16682288,-0.41136724,-0.0027533064,-0.2329535,0.47482932,-0.10976683,-0.2281231,0.19117238,0.115738355,0.38559112,-0.11791144,-0.15087213,0.026249923,0.5936951,0.22543736,-0.09880847,0.39306304,-0.2944501,0.24063654,-0.35299104,0.021189775,-0.07523895,0.2577296,-0.016817411,-0.30717787,0.008958266,0.40034267,0.18422617,-0.08906924,0.4054971,0.05170754,-0.04628394,0.097532414,-0.19905823,-0.09826109,-0.259103,0.12213905,-0.08403623,-0.48536444,-0.23993702,0.35838732,-0.3526764,0.554816,0.116687045,-0.20659482,-0.10969771,0.11686776,-0.012848254,0.22405055,-0.003827555,0.03