f2f46bbf-b236-46e5-8612-ee5af2da7d10	Cungkring	saliwat ka ngingetkeun ka batur urang nu ngabogan awak begang, tapi di bogor anu ngan cungkring téh nyéta sajenis dahar anu bisa di sebut loba nu mikaresep. dahar ieu mangrupa potongan kulit sapi anu di asakan maké bungbu konéng. bésa cungkring dahar maké leupeut atawa buras anu guyur sambel kacang. kadang sok di barengan tempé jeung oncom goréng tipung. nu dagang cungkring umum nguriling tuluy pangkal di hiji tempat, saperti pasar-pasar, sakola, ,jeung lokasi lén anu loba kaliwat ku jelema. gorobag ganganana mangrupa kayu sagi nu kaca supaya urang leuwih gampang pilih kulit anu dipikahayang. bésa dahar maké tékor don co, tuluy maké seumat nyéré keur ngadaharna gaganti séndok. rasa legit jeung gurih, tur seungit bungbu konéngna gé. tapi aya ogé cungkring nu geus di iran siga saté nu dibeuleum, tapi cungkring mah heunteu dibeuleum. di bogor loba pisan nu dagang cungkring tapi bésa mah lolobana di pasar-pasar tradisional jeung tukang dahar jajan pasar.	http://majalah-balebat.blogspot.com/2009/09/cungkring.html	154	[-0.5899362,-0.2378697,-0.056612972,0.19038637,0.095580705,-0.2559079,-0.3024564,-0.016166765,0.108850986,0.3508725,-0.4603691,0.65409255,0.09332852,-0.5403143,0.35357505,-0.2771681,0.2888483,-0.1654636,0.7574643,0.041705422,-0.040941074,0.09601668,-0.05766988,0.37105814,0.07965064,-0.2134552,-0.15572493,0.5845989,0.20401958,-0.12440779,0.41403902,-0.14130525,0.05057055,-0.21110493,-0.15689234,-0.03904464,0.11721841,-0.068141244,-0.1915362,0.05209397,-0.11376007,0.08168356,-0.05949279,0.5504479,0.25916168,0.15068135,0.15093958,-0.3193613,0.077413954,-0.25158668,0.1093573,-0.23161244,-0.3506654,-0.39538226,0.461718,-0.4963992,0.6130077,-0.10580093,-0.28005832,-0.21441601,0.14426191,0.12421376,0.16611277,-0.088420026,-0.12839442,0.13631478,0.27447653,0.06874395,-0.516918,-0.098818995,-0.22850204,0.061389275,-0.36476582,-0.098264754,-0.13216995,-0.030796105,0.021948962,0.62584877,-0.010457988,0.29560438,-0.24316397