wasna beueus atawa rada baseuh sarta kurang cahya matapoé. tingali hal ieu, anton ferdénto, panalungtik ti balai arkéologi bandung boga dugan, guha-guha ieu leutik mungkin pernah guna jadi dumuk ku manusa zaman buhun. “lamun seug kungsi aya aktivitas manusa di dieu, paling ogé ngan samentara waktu. upama jadi tempat reureuh atawa tempat keur ngiuhan,” tambah anton. inya ogé teu manggihan tuduh aya aktivitas zaman buhun di dadasar guha bagi jerona. mémang can kabéh guha nu aya di gunung sodong ider ku tim survéy, ngan lamun tilik kana hasil panalungtikan nu geus laku di guha-guha nu aya di wilayah ieu, can panggih aya urut kagétan budaya mangsa buhun, teges zaman néolitik nu luyu jeung pakakas nu timu dina prosés ékskavasi.	http://majalah-balebat.blogspot.com/2013/04/guha-di-gunung-sodong-urut-padumukan.html	427	[-0.5507612,-0.3245547,0.05649902,0.34825367,0.10361361,-0.111807615,-0.28245795,-0.008468933,0.09260699,0.308026,-0.42123467,0.5236496,0.11513306,-0.5069826,0.31214035,-0.32280827,0.27865434,-0.20674539,0.49555454,-0.06379638,-0.22762248,0.034706526,0.0008558538,0.26376578,-0.033511102,-0.21957241,-0.024241578,0.50274295,0.18741927,-0.19251904,0.5185436,-0.20490597,0.24884045,-0.23072198,0.036825534,-0.025029158,0.0132376,0.06888546,-0.3198943,0.006420765,-0.14964902,0.18701261,-0.23357397,0.45123398,0.117708884,-0.11454984,0.07090005,-0.13471396,-0.00940362,-0.24517474,0.08739243,-0.14618924,-0.45279163,-0.20439029,0.36693954,-0.38851076,0.52779096,-0.05413577,-0.18777797,-0.2727003,0.14803743,0.026434537,0.2438184,0.0804797,-0.17626211,-0.05504863,0.36488253,-0.079737194,-0.45664996,-0.016366107,-0.18364874,0.029911932,-0.5202878,-0.20524375,-0.15512015,-0.04565598,0.0816665,0.48013544,0.11855329,0.4497083,-0.16208634,-0.12987739,0.3915768,0.32605672,-0.19727477,0.19070536,-0.17325015,0.5307028,0.062222607,0.26411647,0.2169368,-0.26674128,0.23438585,-0.04818552,-0.30212277,0.35825256,-0.26688004,-0.06348295,0.22526509,0.4746589,0.4961629,0.0072418973,0.116