a9cbc2c8-e458-4c06-be1c-7cb981f7ae3d	Jaipongan Geus Ngakar	bandung -- geus tilu puluh ton seni tari jaipongan tumuwuh sarta ngakar di tatar sunda, komo lor negeri, dina hal ieu di amérika jeung walanda. dina mimiti tuwuh di ahir 1970-1980-an, tari anu cipta ku gugum gumbira tirasondjaya ieu, anggap minangka seni tari anu boga konotasi négatif alatan ngeksplorasi bagén-bagén sénsitip awak awéwé. padahal, gerak rupa éta tumuwuh subur dina tari rahayat basisir. "kanyatanana, tari jaipongan éta henteu kitu. seni tari anu kreasi ku mestro tari jaipong gugum gumbira nyéta karya seni anyar dina dunya tari sunda, anu sar-sarnya henteu ngan cokot ti penca-silat, tapi ti sagala rupa seni tari rahayat anu tumuwuh di sakuléh wewengkon di jawa barat," ceuk eka gandara, aktor teater sohor ti bandung, di sesela acara "gumbira sareng kang gugum: nyukcruk jaipongan ti sungapanana," anu laksana ku bale rumawat padjadjaran unpad, digawé beng jeung bank jabar sarta lingkung seni jugala, minggu (20/6) di taman bale rumawat padjadjaran, unpad, jln. dipati ukur-bandung. eka, jaba dipikawanoh minangka aktor ogé dipikawanoh laku ahli karawitan, anu neuleuman seni tradisional , asup silat di jerona. hadir tari jaipongan anu dina waktu éta meunang hahalang anu cukup kot ti pemda jabar sarta inohong-inohong masarakat, sieun gugum gumbira tarik napas sarta ngayakeun lawan ku cara gerilya, nyéta ngadegkeun sangar-sanggar jaipongan di sakuléh jawa barat. jaba ti éta, latih jaipongan ka jumlah guru kasenén di meh unggal kota di jawa barat. "kuring asup jelema anu ngarojong gugum, waktu éta ambéh henteu putus harepan. kuring ngerahkan sakabeh guru kasenén tradisional pikeun ajar tari jaipongan," ceuk inohong pendidikan dana saté ieu. "dasar-dasar tari rahayat sarta silat mangrupa inti gerak ti tari jaipongan. ti heula saméméh kuring nyiptakeun tari jaipongan, kuring nyiptakeun tari ketuk tilu pergolan, anu tampik ku masarakat tari. tari sebut terus kuring kembangkan deui sarta dibéré ngaran tari jaipongan," ceuk gugum gumbira. peuting éta, tari jaipongan keur bubuka acara nyéta tari jaipong don pulus keser bojong bawak ku neneng en ca tunggal, lay tabuhan musik wit gap samba sunda. sanggeus éta susul ku panampilan rita tila, anu mawa do lagu karya gugum nu kakoncara, nyéta serat salira jeung bulan sapasi. karya gugum anu pidang dina acara kasebut, jaba keser bojong jeung kawung anten, oge rawayan sarta penjug bojong. kum karya tari sebut bawak lay alus ku anak boh sarta asuhanana. jaba ti éta, pidang ogé tari jaipong kembang ujung, hasil daya kreasi anak boh gugum, nyéta karya awan métro ti padepokan sekar panggung.	http://majalah-balebat.blogspot.com/2010/06/jaipongan-geus-ngakar.html	399	[-0.43370527,-0.27131185,-0.0037398753,0.31606862,0.21405354,-0.076880485,-0.16840851,0.064972624,0.24456397,0.29077095,-0.46899658,0.6294532,0.016297432,-0.5887853,0.3189991,-0.29426596,0.26699027,-0.1744245,0.57007504,-0.11840189,-0.15169388,0.114681825,0.09947494,0.23075117,0.09242939,-0.12747137,-0.16069809,0.563508,0.31247288,-0.16253546,0.29171622,-0.2571367,0.100212455,-0.23577268,0.07537806,0.052811738,-0.014611587,-0.032823846,-0.21855685,0.023026038,0.28201836,0.26573017,-0.16005763,0.5882858,0.18134142,-0.0780497,0.1534676,-0.31500763,0.06373614,-0.21062124,0.11362024,-0.16641091,-0.27926445,-0.430758,0.49784726,-0.57952195,0.6552106,0.19564061,-0.31378168,-0.07316357,0.1924651,0.098449305,0.15497155,0.12267735,-0.025035303,-0.029124375,0.40612468,-0.021170113,-0.36320513,-0.19869936,-0.19818227,0.15193439,-0.27179956,-0.07920549,-0.13937594,-0.0632542,-0.1462881,0.6445239,0.04479824,0.25507823,-0.11805586,-0.09428552,0.2854666,0.17354427,-0.26957786,0.21913481,-0.049784243,0.5404284,0.17374164,0.3132518,0.23298931,-0.3629927,0.30598432,0.06109064,-0.24051285,0.24992245,-0.208501,-0.1208176,0.23390168,0.49254727,0.51255107,0.022058517,0.31017464,-0.13207202,-0.1554119,-0.087451234,-0.45692432,0.36956063,-0.032882128,-0.18578729,0.23429744,-0.4112795,-0.06458244,-