ab3ece43-5491-46f6-b526-85d07a9379cf	Kariaan Cap Go Méh Siap Digelar di Bogor	acara karéan cap go méh di kota bogor baris langsung poé senén (6/2/2012) puseur di kelenténg hok ték bio atawa vihara nagun jalan surya kenca nomor 1, kelurahan babakan pasar, kecamatan bogor tengah, kota bogor. rencana acara ieu baris hadir ku gupernur jawa barat ahmad héryawan katut walikota bogor ani budérto. karéan cap go méh nu baris gel téh mangrupa kombinasi acara ritol warga tionghoa sarta hélaran rupa atraksi seni budaya. acara hélaran mimiti jam 16.30 soré sanggeus upacara panariman tamu penting ti lor kota. lén ti gotong joli-joli nu eusi arca para déwa, hélaran ieu bakal diramékeun ku rupa atraksi seni. sagédéngeun ti atraksi barong jeung liong nu geus bésa tandang, sarta seni calung jeung angklung, ogé bakal midang kasenén ti tanah papo. lén ti éta, baris tampil ogé atraksi kasenén kilin. atraksi seni kilin kawilang langka panggih di indonesé, komo di wilayah bogor mah. di hélaran cap go méh ieu, seni kilin rék tampil ku kumpul gerak badan (pgb) bango putih bogor. has féstival cap go méh bogor jimmy nyebutkeun, yén kilin téh percaya laku sato tutumpakan para déwa anu cipta ti 13 unsur sasatoan, kaya tanduk peucang, buntut kuya, kulit naga, jst. panjang jalan surya kancana baris jadi rute hélaran, ti mimiti kelenténg hok ték bio tepi ka vihara buddhasena. diperkirakeun acara baris réngsé jam 24.00 tengah peuting.	http://majalah-balebat.blogspot.com/search/label/ANGKLUNG%20GUBRAG	221	[-0.49507707,-0.25451255,0.058862444,0.21498598,0.1271672,-0.047095217,-0.15298331,0.11162485,0.06872828,0.11768997,-0.4549476,0.54553264,0.1390053,-0.5957967,0.33762315,-0.287633,0.045848094,-0.19072765,0.54937106,-0.18955803,-0.16316283,0.25666448,0.074779555,0.31175894,0.04845596,-0.18590033,-0.29295716,0.8172772,0.28209895,-0.12637639,0.3100564,-0.19820929,0.17584772,-0.17916732,0.0062086605,0.008254383,0.12486649,-0.040303074,-0.21577385,0.08976477,0.30939013,0.12531933,-0.14310008,0.49417812,