bd885de2-afd2-43e3-aa2e-35c5c5c5559e	Marelak Awi dina Poé Awi Sadunya	ga loba jalma tacan nyaho 18 séptémber geus tetep ku organisasi awi sa-dunya (world bamboo organization wbo) minangka poé awi sadunya. maksud ditetepkeunana hal ieu sangkan bisa ningkatkeun sadar masarakat kana penting mangpat awi keur hirup di sakuléh dunya. di tingkat nasional, kampanyeu penting awi sakaligus miéling poé awi dunya bener geus laku pamaréntah, dina hal ieu mentri lingkung hidup (klh) ti ton ka tukang. harita pamaréntah baris ngembangkeun poténsi leuweung awi laku tangkal anu bisa jaga ékosistim jeung konsérvasi sumber cai baku di sakuléh indonésé. lila ieu, kakara provinsi bali anu gap sarta ngembangkeun leuweung awi kalawan enya-enya. tempat di gényar, bali aya leuweung awi anu lega 500 héktar anu dikokolakeun ku pamaréntah tempat husus pikeun konsérvasi sumber cai. sagédéngeun boga niléy ekologis jeung mangpat konsérvasi cai, awi ogé boga niléy ékonomi nu kacida gedéna. ku kitu pihak klh nyarankeun ka pihak provinsi sangkan ngalaksanakeun program ieu lay ré. ngan gana, kampanyeu pamaréntah kait penting awi keur kahirupan, ogé ngeunan poé awi dunya can tepi ka masarakat di tingkat handap. kitu ogé kagétan nu kait jeung miéling poé awi dunya sepi warta ku médé. padahal aya sababaraha élémén masarakat nu henteu wé ngan ukur miéling poé awi ieu, tapi sakaligus ogé ngayakeun kagétan nyata pelak bibit awi di budeur lingkunganana. dina poé ahad (22/9/13) sahenteuna aya do tempat di wilayah bogor anu ngalaksanakeun kagétan pelak bibit awi masal kait miéling poé awi sadunya. anu ka-hiji di désa ciomas rahayu, kecamatan ciomas jeung nu ka-do di kampung budaya ndangbarang (kbs), désa pasir eurih, kecamatan tamansari. donana aya di wilayah kabupatén bogor. kagétan pelak awi di désa ciomas rahayu kokojo ku kampoeng belajar, hiji lembaga swadaya masarakat nu paduli kana atik masarakat di lor sakola. dina kagétan ieu kampoeng belajar gawé bareng jeung komunitas bambu nusantara sarta banten creatif community (bcc). katémbong warga, ti budak tepi ka kolot, gotongroyong marelak awi nu bibit geus disadékeun ku pihak bcc. dina kasempetan ieu dédén wibawa, pupuhu kampoeng belajar ngajéntrékeun, maksud kagétan ieu sangkan bisa mucunghulkeun sadar masarakat kana penting guna awi nu dipelak. “ku sabab awi boga loba mangpat, boh keur konsérvasi, nyumponan perlu keur sandang, pangan, jeung paimahan, ogé boga guna keur kaséhatan. cindek awi téh boga niléy ékonomi nu hadé,” teges dédén. samentara di kbs, tutas acara pelak awi beng di budeur kbs, warga ogé ajak milu acara diskusi ngeunan penting awi keur kahirupan. acara diskusi nu tempat di balé riung kbs ieu, hadir ku pupuhu kbs maki sumawijaya, para aktivis lingkungan, jeung warga satempat. laku narasumber dina acara diskusi ieu, nyéta kang muqodas ti bcc.	http://majalah-balebat.blogspot.com/2013/09/marelak-awi-dina-poe-awi-sadunya.html	425	[-0.53528446,-0.34769863,0.030934658,0.27910265,0.0573762,-0.1444658,-0.29628402,-0.047965672,0.1769336,0.10010901,-0.48555043,0.65927005,0.031037686,-0.5678551,0.24331652,-0.3019963,0.10078885,-0.16767421,0.6076036,-0.048871465,-0.17348798,0.12927961,-0.014959807,0.29595292,-0.10588377,-0.05172768,-0.1598787,0.6550016,0.24066946,-0.2181696,0.41925013,-0.164913,0.21827039,-0.30529904,-0.035874486,-0.009561415,0.03776203,-0.026490252,-0.24454327,0.11780982,0.049924213,0.2472482,-0.21313262,0.4551825,0.25372034,-0.13833313,0.22933142,-0.26218557,0.05225203,-0.18624158,0.118027814,-0.18454957,-0.5165182,-0.38142723,0.47723398,-0.5753931,0.47676402,0.03465311,-0.21462815,-0.15572268,0.16397351,0.017570345,0.17718643,0.09439862,-0.052374236,0.017853798,0.30168262,-0.044944417,-0.47850996,-0.26214904,-0.1647962,0.2059994,-0.45562464,-0.17495057,-0.14639507,-0.03704771,-0.041502822,0.7078657,0.16234156,0.32198477,-0.2059815,-0.17033142,0.33528322,0.33740363,-0.27650797,0.14296362,0.038386613,0.63249606,0.19695023,0.4139894,0.24183773,-0.32122368,0.28034818,0.007189881,-0.24437153,0.318