7a317322-7d81-4f5d-bb2e-15ff61f6763b	Ngahirupkeun Deui "Kaulinan Urang Lembu	kotak-kotak téh gambar di luhur taneuh maké kapur bodas. rizal (9) ajleng-ajlengan ti kotak hiji ka kotak-kotak saterusna. babaturanana sakola di sdn sanggrah 3, kec. cilawu, kab. garut aya anu ulin gatrik, pérépét jéngkol, rorodan, tepi ka sorodot gaplok. réntétan kolan tradisional sunda sebut sampak basa ayak pasanggiri kolan budak urang lembur di lapang ngamplang, désa cimaragas, camat cilawu, garut, rebo (12/5). cacak dina téma kolan barudak, pamilonna henteu ngan barudak, nu geus déwasa gé aya nu milu ilubiung kana acara éta, minangka bagi ti tilu belas pamilon wawakil camat sa-kab. garut. gelaran pasanggiri kolan budak ieu mangrupa salah hiji usaha pikeun ngamumulé kolan tradisional. sabab, kiwari budak leuwih gumbira aya di heup layar komputer ngulinkeun kolan online atawa ulin tangkas liwat pakakas saperti playstation, nintendo jsté, sedeng kolan budak tradisional mimiti kapohokeun. "ngaliwatan kolinan, urang, ti mimiti budak tepi ka kolot, ajar pikeun mikanyah budaya sunda," ceuk wakil bupati garut diky candra. kolan anu dilombakan, mimiti ku sondah, gatrik, pérépét jéngkol, bebedilan, rorodan, kelom batok, jajangkungan, sarta éngklé. keur nangtukeun nu meunang, pungkas ku kolan sorodot gaplok. di antara kolan nu dipasanggirikeun, bebedilan jadi nu panghéséna. eutik pisan pamilon nu langsung bisa keuna kana sar dina kali némbak. rata-rata kudu ngulang puluh kali. teu aya pamilon nu terus ambek, alatan saran teu keuna bé. pamustunganana manéhna teu neruskeun usaha sabab lawan geus hontal gurat leuwih tiheula. kolan bebedilan ieu boga mangpat antara pikeun ngasah konséntrasi budak. kolan budak jaman baheula memang loba, rupa-rupa, sarta euyeub ku ajaran, ceuk légégna mah pinuh ku filosofi. kolan éta mucnghul teu leupas tina lingkung tempat éta budak tumetep. budak anu ngalaman budaya tatanén, joh ti wangun modérn, hirup di tengah sérang (sawah), huma, jeung walungan pasti kungsi ngasan ngulinkeun kolinan-kolinan di luhur. lila aya amparan taneuh kosong di dinya aktivitas ulin baris dipigawé, terus sanajan peuting geus manjing gé. wewengkon garut anu wewengkon mangrupa sérang, ladang, jeung walungan di mana-mana. tapi, dina hirup nyata, kolan sebut kiwari geus singkir ku jaman. bareng jeung ngilesna amparan lapang tempat ulin, panerus nu ngulinkeun kolan baheula gé milu leungit. bésa ulin mimiti robah, bareng jeung sumarambahna téknologi visol modérn, nu napak ka unggal wewengkon.	http://majalah-balebat.blogspot.com/2010/05/ngahirupkeun-deui-kaulinan-urang-lembur.html	358	[-0.47670764,-0.27846712,-0.027788198,0.2085478,0.09645082,-0.116614595,-0.08783875,0.017425582,0.15252547,0.1661023,-0.5504393,0.55361915,0.12602834,-0.526064,0.37039077,-0.21400803,0.17255199,-0.27523512,0.6871809,-0.018715164,-0.11053078,0.14397702,0.07100651,0.20088449,0.108306035,-0.14635225,-0.2509855,0.6872328,0.34324557,-0.13702396,0.42863488,-0.19615316,0.11433395,-0.234556,0.068930455,-0.024600865,0.07175625,-0.1651663,-0.21243897,0.09671401,0.17102724,0.18723026,-0.19679615,0.5488889,0.19689599,0.03776578,0.2277745,-0.2602871,0.023032803,-0.2688533,-0.01611746,-0.17251371,-0.3486595,-0.2895517,0.5247305,-0.48960865,0.6674216,0.08595735,-0.32696715,-0.13200325,0.21751532,0.14327502,0.057175864,0.021282304,-0.13331793,-0.00854443,0.27193946,0.016288,-0.3935942,-0.08524457,-0.24450117,0.08432298,-0.4949893,-0.043030843,-0.11747166,0.072355874,-0.06505451,0.6525789,0.007942414,0.39193702,-0.09022489,-0.07142776,0.27574635,0.12407909,-0.35510397,0.32586265,-0.14262977,0.5016293,0.08424011,0.18243036,0.26892498,-0.37866288,0.3405517,-0.038335018,-0.25599927,0.24623328,-0.24866077,-0.20655337,0.18695436,0.54933316,0.51615727,0.0368739,0.20519274,-0.013034945,-0.1754047,-0.19329563,-0.39561844,0.37367535,-0.035927743,-0.105417594,0.2478599,-0.4165476,-0.15835609,-0.14416493,0.54211575,0.18447539,0.057996787,0.2211484,-0.04051363,-0.123702556,-0.47874886,0.1608788,-0.09195504