d17c2973-85d1-46b5-9388-0b139560cabd	Serut Batu jeung Obsidian di Puncak Gunung Sodong	dina poé ahad (7/4/13) tim panalungtik gunung sodong nu bentuk ku dines budaya jeung pariwisata (disbudpar) kabupatén bogor mutus sieun kotak kali ékskavasi di puncak gunung sodong. hal ieu dasar hasil survéy ton kamari anu nunjukkeun yén di tempat ieu pisan panggih sababaraha alat serpih tina batu. do kotak ékskavasi ukuran 2 x 2 méter disépkeun. antara kotak ka-hiji jeung kotak ka-do anggang 18 méter. unggal kotak kali dipigawé eutik ku opat urang anu boga pancén séwang-séwangan. aya nu tugas jadi tukang kali, aya nu jadi juru gambar, juru foto, jeung nu nalingakeun barang timon. do poé jeput waktu nu butuh ku tim panalungtik pikeun nutaskeun prosés ékskavasi ieu. jerona taneuh nu kali di unggal kotak ngan ukur tepi ka 60 cm tina beungeut taneuh. eureun tepi ka 60 cm kusabab lapis taneuh geus stéril, geus teu panggih deui barang timonana. tina ékskavasi di puncak gunung sodong ieu timu sababaraha barang, di antarana: serpih nu mangrupa serut tu tina bahan andésit, beubeulahan (fragmén) tu tufa, jeung beubeulahan tu obsidén, ogé tatal (beubeulahan laleutik) tina tu andésit. panggih serut tu dina panalungtikan ieu mingkin negeskeun duga aya aktivitas manusa zaman buhun di puncak gunung sodong. hal ieu luyu jeung hasil panalungtikan saméméhna nu laku ton kaliwat. harita di budeur puncak gunung sodong timu opat serut tu jeung hiji baliung pasasgi nu désah. numutkeun anton ferdénto, panalungtik balai arkéologi (balar) bandung nu tabah kana rupa mikrolit (babaton leutik tinggal zaman buhun), serut tu nu panggih di gunung sodong ieu mangrupa tu alat digawé manusa zaman néolitik. serut tu nu ukuranana teu leuwih ti 5 cm ieu bisa dipaké keur nyését kulit kayu atawa nyését kulit sato nu rék ala gingna, bisa ogé paranti sieun pakakas nu tungtung keut, tina kayu atawa awi saperti tumbak, upama keur moro binatang. lén ti serut batu, panggih oge beubeulahan leutik tina tu obsidén. ilaharna, obsidén aya di tempat-tempat anu leuwih handap, da tu ieu mah mangrupa hasil tina bituna gunung neu. timu obsidén di puncak gunung sodong, numutkeun dr. johan arif, geolog ti itb bandung,gedé mungkin tu ieu bawa ti dérah lebak ka puncak gunung ku manusa baheula. hanjakalna, tu obsidén nu panggih téh ngan ukur beubeulahan nu ukuranana laleutik, lain mangrupa dina wangun anu maneuh, saperti alat digawé zaman heubeul. “mungkin bé tadi mah ngarupa kénéh, ngan kusabab aya aktivitas zaman ka béhdieunakeun saperti kagétan ngolah taneuh keur kebun di éra kolonél, ahirna batu-batu ieu ancur jadi laleutik,” terang johan. ngeunan kronologi waktu nu pasti mémang can bisa ditangtukeun, sabab kudu ngaliwatan prosés balitungan isotop c-14 tina areng nu panggih nalika ékskavasi. bener dina ékskavasi harita, panggih ogé sésa areng atawa bagi taneuh anu duga ngakandung areng.	http://majalah-balebat.blogspot.com/2013/04/serut-batu-jeung-obsidian-di-puncak.html	442	[-0.5478809,-0.24687608,0.15607858,0.3027489,0.16745284,-0.18345585,-0.24080044,-0.114142254,0.257927,0.25093955,-0.46934223,0.61845744,0.02016099,-0.5271646,0.27405366,-0.2394832,0.22836784,-0.21198937,0.5962169,-0.08345789,-0.1518048,0.08754231,0.02457024,0.252138,-0.11080362,-0.23511519,-0.13384452,0.58787,0.29609782,-0.19738477,0.4571238,-0.19903207,0.1973249,-0.36913598,0.007889926,-0.045372263,0.17980841,-0.06744139,-0.35138333,0.079368725,0.07134177,0.165261,-0.24112001,0.5143336,0.2993093,-0.05489999,0.10717957,-0.19796374,0.0018139279,-0.27479473,0.027123326,-0.10653331,-0.36359906,-0.24341694,0.36471778,-0.4599201,0.5752182,-0.0018078163,-0.23200178,-0.21318582,0.121273555,0.06332828,0.25548863,0.089186534,-0.18599463,-0.002262533,0.40699267,-0.07309636,-0.43369716,-0.1801258,-0.2293905,0.06418396,-0.4930098,-0.10676639,-0.17724755,-0.0649588,0.031059418,0.5524881,0.13280068,0.3533406,-0.14597547,-0.11451459,0.47281283,0.23643798,-0.28433198,0.11706588,-0.08604802,0.61521035,-0.037973806,0.28053015,0.16383788,-0.312