af1e1511-a37a-4ecd-88fb-2333a4aadeac	Ujungan Jadi Wawakil Kasenian Jabar	kasenén ujungan ti kota bekasi baris ngawakilan propinsi jawa barat dina féstival olahraga tradisional tingkat nasional anu laksana di ambon bulan agustus 2010 engké. putus éta lu sanggeus kasenén ujungan jadi pinunjul dina féstival olahraga tradisional propinsi jabar 2009 di lapang tegalega, bandung, (25/11). terang ku pupuhu panata calagara, gg gunawan, kasenén ujungan hasil ngéléhkeun kasenén séjén anu pinton dina festival anu langsung do poé ieu kawas bénjang ti kota bandung atawa golémpang jibrut ti kota bogor. "panenton pinunjul dasar kana orisinalitas emas kasenén, sarta aspék séjén anu peunteun téh kawas bobot atikan, olahraga, musik, sakaligus ogé sisi hiburanana," ceuk gg ngajéntrékeun. pupuhu sanggar seni putra budaya, edi badeng, ngungkabkeun kasanggupanana pikeun tandang di ambon engké. manéhna baris nyép pinton anu leuwih alus nginget pamilon anu séjén baris datang ti propinsi anu béda. nurutkeun hasil féstival ieu, aya genep tandang ti sakuléh jabar nu makalangan, nyéta ujungan ti kota bekasi, golémpang jibrut ti kota bogor, bénjang ti kota bandung, ménpo cikalong ti kabupatén cénjur, ronggéng gunung ti kabupatén cémis, sarta gorol ti kabupatén sukabumi.	http://majalah-balebat.blogspot.com/2009/11/ujungan-jadi-wakil-kasenian-jabar.html	174	[-0.50563943,-0.28849858,0.014278655,0.2606319,0.20493853,-0.112170234,-0.12409825,0.00015789647,0.16726708,0.23519018,-0.48641306,0.52577317,0.06413675,-0.6056154,0.35800782,-0.27125588,0.1542948,-0.29190797,0.4959632,-0.14069423,-0.10394066,0.24021037,0.16513334,0.2546274,0.13529597,-0.15633138,-0.25256962,0.66248524,0.3049314,-0.24852227,0.36515582,-0.28701508,0.21478759,-0.2161759,0.007435485,-0.026056606,0.21646266,-0.14225593,-0.12192649,0.072836705,0.29618314,0.20554756,-0.23103857,0.53145164,0.15901831,-0.07771716,0.076786414,-0.26817393,-0.101116166,-0.124246456,0.062265407,-0.15653244,-0.3822306,-0.34964493,0.47404462,-0.6415484,0.684