70b19437-ecae-4246-92da-a16a3e9cfc2b	Urang Baduy Jero Ngarayakeun Talari Kawalu	lebak —warga suku baduy jero kabupatén lebak, propinsi banten, jumah (5/3/2010), ngarayakeun talari kawalu do atawa "bulan karo" pinuh basajan alatan tacan sakumnana warga usum panén paré huma. "acara ieu pinuh ku ka husyuk sarta do ménta kayan nagara aman, tengtrem, sarta sejahtera," ceuk sekretaris désa kanekes, camat leuwidamar, kabupatén lebak, sarpin. sarpin ngomong, aya kawalu pikeun warga baduy jero anu cicing di kampung cibeo sarta cikawartana, désa kanekes, sedeng kampung cikeusik geus ngarayakeun dina poé kemis (4/3/2010). tilu lembur baduy jero eta laksana lay pinuh basajan. warga ngarayakeunana lay pinuh khidmat sarta husyuk bari do ménta ka pangéran anu maha kawasa ambéh nagara ieu aman, tengtrem, sarta sejahtera. "lamun nagara ieu aman sarta tengtrem tangtu masarakat baris sejahtera," manéhna ménta lila kawalu lumangsung, nu datang teu meunang asup ka lembur baduy dina alatan keur ngalaksanakeun ibadah sanggeus posa sapoé jeput. ku sabab éta, ceuk manéhna, pihak minangka aparat pamaréntah geus masangkeun peringatan di panto gerbang baduy di ciboleger ambéh nu datang tat hukum adat. sabab, talari kawalu mangrupa putus adat anu kudu laksana saban ton, dirayakan tilu kali lila tilu bulan lay posa sapoé jeput. aya kawalu mangrupa salah hiji talari ritol anu percaya ku warga baduy jero ku kitu perlu ngahargan sarta ngahormatan yakin agem anu anut maranéhanana. numutkeun sarpin "salila ngalaksanakeun kawalu, kayan kampung baduy jero jempling alatan maranéhanana posa sarta loba pilih cicing di imah-imah," wawakil lembaga hukum adat baduy jero, ayah mursid, ngaku, pihak menta hampura alatan lila aya kawalu lembur baduy jero wengku cikawartana, cikeusik, sarta cibeo tutup pikeun nu tang, saha we arek éta pajabat wewengkon atawa pajabat nagara. "kami ngajalankeun kawalu alatan tilar adat sarta kudu ditati," cenah. nurutkeun manéhna, sanggeus lekasan aya kawalu, tangtu nu datang balik kaci ngadatangan wewengkon baduy jero. manéhna ngécéskeun, sanggeus kawalu, hiji bulan anu baris datang ngarayakeun acara seba lay ngadatangan bupati sarta gubernur banten lay mawa hasil-hasil bumi (tatanén). "ayeuna sawaréh warga baduy geus panén paré huma," cenah. manéhna nambahan, aya seba éta minangka salah hiji wangun silaturahim anu kudu dijalin lay alus ka pamaréntah.	http://majalah-balebat.blogspot.com/2010/03/urang-baduy-jero-ngarayakeun-talari.html	340	[-0.44951898,-0.32918158,-0.009742945,0.29072928,-0.0011859834,-0.15443842,-0.17269251,0.011441931,0.18921705,0.1780037,-0.47607234,0.5121163,0.24617873,-0.6362655,0.26358086,-0.22218627,0.2131268,-0.28722477,0.6468183,-0.14309022,-0.27000058,0.16760379,0.12417786,0.29349053,-0.032856457,-0.1425536,-0.23701859,0.7319186,0.16276881,-0.26704535,0.3443263,-0.074188896,0.15738997,-0.2511308,0.03766265,0.1272766,0.07581669,-0.028316053,-0.35462946,-0.10058686,0.17265837,0.07933459,-0.27716124,0.4459436,0.2002805,-0.022902856,0.23289263,-0.33327425,-0.010417648,-0.29173285,0.11152904,-0.15695691,-0.29986492,-0.2682733,0.42932886,-0.53622115,0.58470464,0.16999592,-0.31812316,-0.14347067,0.2569947,0.06825282,0.10952568,0.033119634,0.007138949,-0.057314824,0.34069297,0.016302522,-0.4227248,-0.2710864,-0.118574955,0.12967895,-0.27802163,-0.17302987,-0.16456342,-0.04278268,-0.025081877,0.66955274,0.058837604,0.322721,-0.22255042,-0.07590818,0.24128708,0.29578054,-0.37995148,0.3535763,-0.06632593,0.70423555,0.17991576,0.197136,0.3501971,-0.25152972,0.24241313,0.16342935,-0.300567,0.2647779,-0.14776587,-0.14390329,0.13958141,0.50505614,0.52113605,-0.017568765,0.18422177,-0.19812268,-0.18734154,-0.14300995,-0.33610392,0.46382833,-0.009008287,-0.07943403,0.30122602,-0.49131912,-0.17266297,-0.28961235,0.4297277,0.19198564,-0.019259527,0.1850375,-0.043945078,-0.055335775,-0.55250925,0.25783148,-0.13441443,-0.11403756,-0.10740784,0.36321968,-0.071101815,-0.25251806,0.47996333,-0.06290589,0.2057314,0.36713994,-0.09742156,-0.1